236        private final int r, g, b;
237        private final String name;
238
239        RalColor(int r, int g, int b) {
240                this.r = r;
241                this.g = g;
242                this.b = b;
243                this.name = null;
244        }
245        
246        RalColor(int rgb, String name) {
247                Color c = new Color(rgb);
248                this.r = c.getRed();
249                this.g = c.getGreen();
250                this.b = c.getBlue();
251                this.name = name;
252        }
253
254        @Override
255        public Color getColor() {
256                return new Color(r, g, b);
257        }
258        
259        public String getName() {
260                return this.name;
261        }

273                
274        public static Color[] getColors(RalColor... wcols) {
275                Color[] rgbColors = new Color[wcols.length];
276                for (int i = 0; i < wcols.length; i++) {
277                        rgbColors[i] = wcols[i].getColor();
278                }
279                return rgbColors;
280        }
